    au < released ; 2012-2024 ; Relict Hominoid Inquiry Comments & Responses ; Comments & Responses ; comments--responses >
    au < released ; 2012-2024 ; Relict Hominoid Inquiry Brief Communications ; Brief Communications ; brief-communications >
    au < released ; 2012-2024 ; Relict Hominoid Inquiry Essays ; Essays ; essays >
    au < released ; 2012-2024 ; Relict Hominoid Inquiry News & Views ; News & Views ; news--views >
    au < released ; 2012-2024 ; Relict Hominoid Inquiry Book Reviews ; Book Reviews ; book-reviews >


